videos.description: LeBron James bounces a behind-the-back pass to Marc Gasol, who pulls up from downtown and knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's behind-the-back pass leads to Gasol 3-pointer) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's behind-the-back pass leads to Gasol 3-pointer

videos.description: LeBron James pulls up from the corner and sends the Lakers' bench into a frenzy when he doesn't watch his shot go in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron doesn't need to watch this 3-pointer drop) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron doesn't need to watch this 3-pointer drop

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker is off the mark on his shot, but Montrezl Harrell quickly drives in for a putback reverse dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harrell cleans up THT's miss with reverse jam) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harrell cleans up THT's miss with reverse jam

videos.description: After stealing the ball, Kentavious Caldwell-Pope breaks away to the basket for a dunk, but his attempt bounces off the rim.
videos.headline: KCP misses wide-open dunk

videos.description: Anthony Davis emphatically denies Sterling Brown of a dunk attempt and then mean mugs afterward.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD mean mugs after huge block) 2021/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD mean mugs after huge block

videos.description: LeBron James scores 26 points to go with eight rebounds and five assists in the Lakers' 117-100 win over the Rockets.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (LeBron's 26 points help Lakers cruise past Rockets) 2021/01/12 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LeBron's 26 points help Lakers cruise past Rockets

videos.description: James Harden addresses the media after the Rockets' blowout loss to the Lakers, saying that he doesn't think Houston's situation can be fixed before walking out of the news conference.

videos.headline: Harden: 'We're just not good enough'

videos.description: John Wall describes how he and James Harden are fitting in together on the Rockets.
